      "comment_id" : 137714830,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "When you <i>assign</i> the value you have to use a qualified access like <code>day = Day.Monday;</code> (or use an <code>import static …</code>), however in case of <code>switch</code>, the <code>case</code> labels must use simple names, i.e. <code>switch(day) { case MONDAY: … break; case FRIDAY: … break; }</code>"
