    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You might be using the enums incorrectly in the switch cases. In comparison with the above example by CoolBeans.. you might be doing the following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>switch(day) {\n    case Day.MONDAY:\n        // Something..\n        break;\n    case Day.FRIDAY:\n        // Something friday\n        break;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Make sure that you use the actual enum values instead of EnumType.EnumValue</p>\n\n<p>Eclipse points out this mistake though..</p>\n"
